      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i did see a doctor for stuff like this before and they just said it was stress or migraines. i really dont want to go to the er if i dont have to, it's so expensive and the wait is terrible. do you think it's actually serious or could it just be a weird migraine aura? i have some extra sumatriptan in my cabinet, should i just take a couple of those and try to sleep it off?",
